    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >哥布林的发现</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻常的早上，你一边吃着早点，一边看着早报：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">--------------------- 危险？财富！ ------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">一周前，在一次远古矿洞的探险中，一只哥布林发现这里存在大量的神秘矿物，然后...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">...最后，他说：那里一定有着无尽的财富！但是...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">（记者：巨魔）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">---------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还没来得及看完哥布林的“忠告”，勇敢的你就打算出发一探究竟！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发射弹珠，撞击弹板得分，达到分数要求即可向更深处突破。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+各种特性的弹板和遗物，探索不同的搭配组合策略，挑战突破极限深度。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每回合仅需10秒，带来爽快又烧脑的游戏体验！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305820/extras/71e81220e609532d11ab6ab3033285ae.poster.avif?t=1772214067\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305820/extras/71e81220e609532d11ab6ab3033285ae.webm?t=1772214067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305820/extras/71e81220e609532d11ab6ab3033285ae.mp4?t=1772214067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
